# FFOccamMcp.Core

## Architecture

- `OccamTranscodeTool` + `OccamProbeTool` + `OccamDigestTool` — MCP tool surfaces
- `TranscodePipeline` + `OccamRouter` — routing; do not bypass for one-off logic
- `IExtractBackend` — HTTP (35s) / Browser (120s)
- `ITranscodePostProcessor` — challenge + thin extract

## Rules

- Native AOT safe: source-generated JSON, no reflection serializers
- UTF-8: `Console.OutputEncoding = UTF-8`; Node spawn must preserve UTF-8
- Test hooks: `#if OCCAM_GATE` only — never ship test-only paths in prod without `#if`
- Extend via seams (`AddOccamCore`, backends, post-processors) — not monolith paste from FFWebMCP

## After edits

```powershell
.\scripts\run-l0-fast.ps1
```

Full gate if router/backends/post-processors changed.
